      <title>敏锐的交易员为可能“关键”的特朗普-哈里斯辩论做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/edgy-traders-gird-for-potentially-pivotal-trump-harris-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯与前总统唐纳德·特朗普首次举行总统辩论之前，投资者正在权衡选举风险，他们比 6 月份特朗普与其曾经的对手乔·拜登总统对决之前更加紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/edgy-traders-gird-for-potentially-pivotal-trump-harris-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦逮捕伊姆兰·汗支持者，局势再度紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/pakistan-arrests-imran-khan-loyalists-stoking-tensions-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦逮捕了前总理伊姆兰·汗所在政党的高层领导人，罪名是在前一天的集会中袭击警察，这加剧了该国的政治冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/pakistan-arrests-imran-khan-loyalists-stoking-tensions-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 06:52:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯面临大规模无人机袭击，莫斯科机场被迫关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/russia-downs-dozens-of-drones-including-near-moscow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯称，周二凌晨共击落了 144 架无人机，其中包括莫斯科地区的无人机，此次袭击导致莫斯科机场的航班暂时停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/russia-downs-dozens-of-drones-including-near-moscow</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 05:39:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及通胀率数月来首次因燃油价格上涨而上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/egypt-inflation-quickens-for-first-time-in-months-on-fuel-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及的通货膨胀在燃料补贴减少后加速，打破了连续五个月的通胀减速趋势，为 2020 年以来的首次降息铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/egypt-inflation-quickens-for-first-time-in-months-on-fuel-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 05:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲为乌克兰最后一批天然气供应做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/europe-braces-for-final-end-of-ukraine-s-russian-gas-deliveries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰拥有超过 22,000 公里的天然气管道，几十年来一直是欧洲能源市场的重要参与者。但到今年年底，这些战略资产可能会陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/europe-braces-for-final-end-of-ukraine-s-russian-gas-deliveries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
